---
title: Easy Pork & Coconut Baked Rice with Ginger, Lemongrass & Crispy Shallots
description: If you haven't tried pork in baked rice before, well, what can we say – you're missing out! Give it a go with this easy, hands-off
recipe, that's studded with crunchy veggies, aromatic ginger and lemongrass and silky baby spinach.

